  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Post is a firm favourite with Inghams' guests who have enjoyed the warm welcome and stylish surroundings of this 'Relais &amp; Chateaux' hotel.Owners Andre and George personally ensure the wellbeing of each of their guests who appreciate the hotel's elegant European atmosphere and excellent cuisine. The wide range of facilities include a sophisticated spa, award winning restaurant and its world renowned wine cellar with over 32,500 bottles and more than 2,200 selections of available wines. The stylish decorated rooms make the Post an excellent choice for discerning guests who seek little extra touches on the finest ski holiday.</p>]]></description>
